name: Abandoned in the Woods
description:
Holda is the main antagonist of the 2020 dark fantasy horror film Gretel and Hansel directed by Oz Perkins
 she was the mother of a young girl who known simply as the Beautiful Child. The child was once ill and enchantress healing her but giving her powers to kill peoples.
Holda attempted to abandon her daughter and leave her on the woods, but she continued to linger in her mind long afterwards. and child promised to share her powers with Holda to killing/devouring her other children.


2000*1500
